Privacy Policy for NMC Prep
Last Updated: April 4, 2025

NMC Prep ("the App") is developed by Nahusha Investment ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy.

1. No Government Affiliation
NMC Prep is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially connected to the Nepal Medical Council (NMC) or any government entity.

The App is an independent educational tool designed to help users prepare for medical exams through multiple-choice questions (MCQs).

2. Information We Collect
We do not collect, store, or share any personal data.

The App does not require users to sign up, provide personal details, or track activity.

3. Permissions Used
The App may request certain device permissions (such as internet access) for core functionality.

However, no personal data is collected or stored.

4. Third-Party Services
The App does not use third-party services (e.g., analytics, ads, tracking tools).

If this changes in the future, we will update this policy and notify users accordingly.

5. Future Changes
If we decide to collect user data in the future, we will:

Update this privacy policy accordingly.

Notify users about any data collection and obtain consent if required.

6. Contact Us
For any questions or concerns, contact us at:
Email: nahushainvestment@gmail.com
